Body:
assert dss.Executive.Command(1) == u'New'
assert dss.Executive.CommandHelp(1).replace(os.linesep, '\n') == u"""Create a new object within the DSS. Object becomes the active object
Example: New Line.line1 ..."""
assert dss.Executive.NumCommands() == 114
assert dss.Executive.NumOptions() == 115
assert dss.Executive.Option(1) == u'type'
assert dss.Executive.OptionHelp(1
    ) == u'Sets the active DSS class type.  Same as Class=...'
assert dss.Executive.OptionValue(1) == u'Line'
